    "Through this integration, the effects of illegal perturbation samples in the feature space are lessened.",
    "Liu and Jin [85] explored the creation of deep neural architectures via a multiobjective evolutionary algorithm that is resistant to five common adversarial attacks.",
    "Furthermore, Pestana et al. [86] presented for the first time a class of robust images that are easy to defend against adversarial attacks and that recover better than random images.",
    "To improve the adversarial robustness of deep hashing models, the focus has been on investigating semantic-aware adversarial training (SAAT) [87].",
